248
00:22:08,530 --> 00:22:11,250
That's something that
makes you wonder:

249
00:22:11,410 --> 00:22:13,570
How did that happen?

250
00:22:13,730 --> 00:22:17,890
Why has the state discovered
feminism all of a sudden

251
00:22:18,050 --> 00:22:22,930
and why do we now have so many
women with children who are working?

252
00:22:23,450 --> 00:22:27,650
So it's really about creating
a more productive society,

253
00:22:27,810 --> 00:22:31,130
about incentives
to make society more productive.

254
00:22:31,330 --> 00:22:35,210
- That's how I see it.
- And to preserve the capitalist system.

255
00:22:35,730 --> 00:22:38,490
- Actually.
