752
00:59:56,210 --> 00:59:59,650
You can do that politically,
socially with incentives

753
00:59:59,810 --> 01:00:01,930
and by supporting that.

754
01:00:02,090 --> 01:00:06,650
To create the possibility of having
those diverse social contacts.

755
01:00:06,810 --> 01:00:10,250
Not by doing the opposite
with urban planning,

756
01:00:10,410 --> 01:00:14,410
that is, keeping people among
their own, in their own schools.

757
01:00:14,570 --> 01:00:18,690
Or, on the other hand, by having
schools that are so diverse

758
01:00:18,850 --> 01:00:21,330
